[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man's body discovered in Cardiff River Taff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man's body has been discovered in the River Taff near Cardiff's Swalec Stadium, police have said.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police have cordoned off an area for the body to be removed from the water.
An investigation is under way to establish the man's identity and the circumstances surrounding his death.
Officers were alerted to the scene at Pontcanna Fields at about 17:30 BST on Friday.
